  "synopsis": "Terminally ill Miena Sidus has the ability to enter other people's dreams. Knowing her time will be up soon, Miena decides to use her power to gather money for her loving parents as a last gesture of gratitude. But as she navigates the dreams, she finds herself involved with a mysterious boy, a young lord, and a great dragon. Moreover, they all seem to need her help and are intent on saving her as well. Will these new relationships change Miena's fate and give her a ray of hope in life?\n\n(Source: Tapas)",
